reviewText: This would only produce sound for the introduction and then nothing!  I tried everything I could think of to restart it, etc. but to no avail.

Im not going to lie, kids love barney. This movie was on net flicks and then they took it off. My kids were very mad, so i looked and amazon. As soon as i found it i bought it. It works great no problems. And to tell you the truth I think this is best of all barneys.
My daughter loves watching this one Barney over and over again.. She has learned so many nursery rhymes and sings them through out the day... Definetly her favorite..the picture quality was great

The "red, yellow, and blue" movie is a little on the old and boring side but the "rhyme time rhythm" makes up for the other movie! Good for a couple bucks... but I won't say this is the best barney movie around!
2 yr old niece loves it. Keeps her busy and she just loves to dance and sing with Barney and friends. Good way for young kids to start learning.
Good price. Good quality. Received in a timely manner.
I love watching Barney and Friends.
